General.Name: Pentanet Ltd
General.Description: Pentanet Limited operates as a telecommunications carrier and internet service provider in Perth, Australia. It operates in two segments, Internet and Telecommunication Services, and Gaming Technology. The company offers fixed wireless network services to residential and business customers. It also provides national broadband network, PentaMAX, XFIBRE, and apartment broadband products, as well as offers Wi-Fi setup services, and business and commercial solutions. Pentanet Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
